cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for document-level sentiment classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses transfer learning, which is a popular technique in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper deals with the use of language models, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the use of hierarchical models, which can be applied to various domains, including information retrieval (cs.IR) and computer vision (cs.CV).
